  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the radiation exposure of scattered radiation for the interventionalist
      during coronary angiography using different X-ray protection materials, namely, an X-ray
      Screen without additional X-ray protection, an X-ray Screen with additional protective strips
      and an X-ray Screen with additional protective strips AND protective patient cut-outs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
